agenda_items.name: 2016 September Minutes
agenda_items.title: Recommendation to approve the Parks & Recreation Commission Meeting minutes of September 15, 2016.

agenda_items.name: 2016 October PSA's
agenda_items.title: Authorize the Director, or his or her management designee, to execute the Personal Services and Instruction Agreements and amend Attachment "A" of the agreements as needed.

agenda_items.name: 2016 October Fee Waivers
agenda_items.title: Recommendation to approve the fee waiver requests outlined in Attachment "A", in accordance with the Fee Waiver policy.

agenda_items.name: 2016 October LAYBS of LB Container
agenda_items.title: Support the relocation of a previously-approved storage container to an existing cement pad in proximity to Field #2 in El Dorado Park West and authorize the Director of Parks, Recreation and Marine to execute an amendment to Right of Entry Permit P-00051, and any other necessary documents, with Los Altos Youth Baseball and Softball of Long Beach, Inc. a California non-profit corporation.  (District 5)

agenda_items.name: 2016 Homland PSA
agenda_items.title: Authorize the Director, or his or her management designee, to execute Personal Service Agreements for Homeland Cultural Center and amend Attachement "a" of the agreements as needed. (District 6)

agenda_items.name: 2016 October WCC
agenda_items.title: Recommendation to receive and file the Director's monthly highlights report, "We Create Community",  for October, 2016.
